Html: On my members/list.aspx page I have 3 testreg members listed, but they do not show up on my users page, I already deleted the default users and created my own user and admin user. How do I delete these members from the member list page?

Jaxjon, You'll need to remove them from the ASP related database tables

aspnet_Membership
aspnet_Users
aspnet_UsersInRoles
dbo.MemberInfo
dbo.MemberProfile
(I think these are the only ones)

Keep in mind that if any of the users own data like message threads, albums, blogs, etc that it could realy hose your site up.  You'll want to delete and data they own as well.

riscfl,
Thank you for your input, I will try this.
jaxjon
